{
  "id": "ch4_opening",
  "slides": [
    {
      "text": "君临城。\n篡夺者战争，终章。",
      "subtext": "",
      "duration": 3.5,
      "scene_art": "red_keep_breach",
      "camera_style": "battle_sway"
    },
    {
      "text": "城门破了。\n不是被攻破的——\n是被打开的。",
      "subtext": "泰温·兰尼斯特的旗帜，\n金色之狮，\n出现在金色的城楼上。",
      "duration": 5.5,
      "scene_art": "red_keep_breach",
      "camera_style": "battle_sway"
    },
    {
      "text": "城内，王室守卫仍在抵抗。\n混战在街道与宫殿的廊柱之间蔓延。",
      "subtext": "奈德勒住缰绳。\n「保护平民。向前。」",
      "duration": 5.0,
      "scene_art": "red_keep_breach",
      "camera_style": "battle_sway"
    },
    {
      "text": "序章·四",
      "subtext": "铁王座",
      "duration": 4.0,
      "scene_art": "red_keep_breach",
      "camera_style": "battle_sway"
    }
  ]
}
